{"tid":2382340,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"算係半個本地花農，今年比年宵搞到死哂，你問我答","createTime":"2021-01-27T08:14:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T21:15:50.000Z","uid":390941,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5fa4f5e5538b8246b6681e7223d30326974e05d8","tid":2382340,"uid":390941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:14:58.000Z","msg":"開個Post 想同大家分享下年宵同本地花 (少量 自己唔係識好多)<br />\n其實最近幾年都唔係好<br />\n但今年真係比政府搞到雞毛鴨血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n拋少少磚先<br />\n點解成日話要買本地花 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實係因為本地花會開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以劍蘭為例，其實任何運過嚟嘅都雪藏過<br />\n因為可以keep住啲花唔會過左時間 (開哂)<br />\n但缺點係支花唔識開到頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以好多賣劍蘭嘅會同你講摘咗個頂佢 先會扯水啊 開得好啲<br />\n真正原因係支花根本就開唔到頂<br />\n<br />\n小弟個A/C 今日先開 應該係計P牌仔<br />\n如果各巴絲有興趣聽落去 麻煩幫手推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b429bdd79dfd10eab3406b4a39fa5f5cc5d819","tid":2382340,"uid":209139,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:17:37.000Z","msg":"有咩本地花品種? 啲苗來源自邊度?"},{"pid":"d5c5924fcfd83a8c543487cc781f509682f6df8c","tid":2382340,"uid":85057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:18:32.000Z","msg":"知唔知西瓜祥近況？"},{"pid":"f72581d887d07788c1718a9e14f45dccc90e7c23","tid":2382340,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:24:54.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔使租做花市咩"},{"pid":"86c79bbb2374893df92bd018abd25a3627297463","tid":2382340,"uid":390941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8b429bdd79dfd10eab3406b4a39fa5f5cc5d819","tid":2382340,"uid":209139,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:17:37.000Z","msg":"有咩本地花品種? 啲苗來源自邊度?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:29:59.000Z","msg":"自己係做桃花 劍蘭<br />\n一般我地桃花個苗就係本地<br />\n有一支冇理過佢嘅花<br />\n佢結果後會有核掉落地 慢慢自然生長到有苗我哋再拎去用<br />\n劍蘭頭就荷蘭<br />\n<br />\n另外本地比較常見應該係菊花 百合<br />\n但種子源自邊就唔清楚"},{"pid":"472c1e011ef2442529bfdaeef3b804ec285fd2e4","tid":2382340,"uid":390941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5c5924fcfd83a8c543487cc781f509682f6df8c","tid":2382340,"uid":85057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:18:32.000Z","msg":"知唔知西瓜祥近況？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:32:12.000Z","msg":"唔識佢真人<br />\n我見過佢果次就係721<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199841c75446b360468f83babdb4002dbdf0f364","tid":2382340,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:32:32.000Z","msg":"有無最靚嘅相"},{"pid":"73c71de3698c7e79ac7b5ea18f703856331ac629","tid":2382340,"uid":390941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f72581d887d07788c1718a9e14f45dccc90e7c23","tid":2382340,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:24:54.000Z","msg":"唔係話唔使租做花市咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:34:15.000Z","msg":"係啊<br />\n但其實我自己好多熟客係年宵搵返你<br />\n咁搞法冇人想行都唔出奇<br />\n同埋免租<br />\n但棚錢之類都係要<br />\n加上消毒都係大問題<br />\n到時支花出事又係自己硬食"},{"pid":"a4ff606dcb53adb9786ff8245fdd9bd3a3182aed","tid":2382340,"uid":14605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:39:09.000Z","msg":"多唔多鄉黑花農"},{"pid":"7f8428d87a3648f9cc5077de3c75eeda35b9b331","tid":2382340,"uid":390941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"199841c75446b360468f83babdb4002dbdf0f364","tid":2382340,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:32:32.000Z","msg":"有無最靚嘅相"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:16:47.000Z","msg":"冇乜影到靚圖<br />\n同埋我做野對得最多係綁好哂 冇左個花型<br />\n比朵花你望下<br />\n唔知啱唔啱巴打心水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNa9Stw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNa9Stw.png&h=dd6034d0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dec05322ffe292d35b535c4659ce3edb7b1b925","tid":2382340,"uid":390941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4ff606dcb53adb9786ff8245fdd9bd3a3182aed","tid":2382340,"uid":14605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T08:39:09.000Z","msg":"多唔多鄉黑花農"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T09:19:03.000Z","msg":"認識嘅都係租田嘅比較多<br />\n不過都知有鄉黑<br />\n個人估計就55 64左右<br />\n鄉黑都知做花農搵唔到食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e866b880475ab696466d6e38cae07acbc10192","tid":2382340,"uid":390941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:28:21.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20856a237a1251b9321e678dcdd38b6099cb4e23","tid":2382340,"uid":390941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9e866b880475ab696466d6e38cae07acbc10192","tid":2382340,"uid":390941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T10:28:21.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T12:59:44.000Z","msg":"好想推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62d232a94d29c951811b627a050508d59ff002e3","tid":2382340,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:32:14.000Z","msg":"銀柳加水就生根<br />\n有咩方法令桃花插水都生根"},{"pid":"960fa119bf0c11ffc4c644557c0a7be727cd988c","tid":2382340,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:34:14.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"00f751105540ad5f03a387d151a804c2634b57e8","tid":2382340,"uid":251207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:34:37.000Z","msg":"想買桃花 但買親都一大棵 冇位擺<br />\n其實有冇啲係會出盆栽Size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"0a9b9ef33e548a03c3e0bd0248af01328cfe8f0d","tid":2382340,"uid":390941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62d232a94d29c951811b627a050508d59ff002e3","tid":2382340,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:32:14.000Z","msg":"銀柳加水就生根<br />\n有咩方法令桃花插水都生根"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:21:48.000Z","msg":"冇方法<br />\n因為桃花根一定係跟樹頭<br />\n就算我地成支插返落去泥土都唔會生<br />\n我地自己種到大支都係由桃苗開始慢慢生根"},{"pid":"dae0b870539508de4ed2b9c44be73407d319abe0","tid":2382340,"uid":390941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"960fa119bf0c11ffc4c644557c0a7be727cd988c","tid":2382340,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T04:34:14.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:22:52.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身以為個post已經沉左冇mon住"},{"pid":"0548aef0f06b809bac8563ca80caa968543f8772","tid":2382340,"uid":390941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"00f751105540ad5f03a387d151a804c2634b57e8","tid":2382340,"uid":251207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-06T08:34:37.000Z","msg":"想買桃花 但買親都一大棵 冇位擺<br />\n其實有冇啲係會出盆栽Size<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:25:04.000Z","msg":"以前係年宵見過話有隻日本桃花係真係係好細個盆<br />\n但係咪堅日本就唔知<br />\n自問都唔識做果種花嘅功夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為土地都會影響花型<br />\n係香港做唔做到果種都難講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf79bcfd4fdc3fb77db6eb1dab1a2f27593c978","tid":2382340,"uid":129378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T16:29:28.000Z","msg":"有無咩花推介？ 行完一轉花市無乜心水，想搵D 少見嘅花，唔想咁大路"},{"pid":"504e8d296e41f3b4740